        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "2.   The development shall be undertaken strictly according to plans enclosed with necessary permission"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "       endorsement."
