        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "3.   Total parking space measuring "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{totalParking}} sq. mtr. ",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": "as shown in the approved plan shall"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "       be exclusively used for parking and no part of it will be used for any other purpose."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "4.   The land over which construction is proposed is accessable by an approved means of access of "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{roadWidth}} mtr. ",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": "width."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "5.   The land in question must be in lawful ownership and peaceful possession of the applicant."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "6.   The applicant shall free gift "
          },
          {
            "text": "{{totalSurrenderRoadArea}} sqm ",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": "wide strip of land to Bhubaneswar Development Authority/ULB for further"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "       widening of the road to the standard width as per CDP-2010, BDA"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "7.   The permission is valid for period of "
          },
          {
            "text": "three years ",
            "bold": true
          },
          {
            "text": "with effect from the date of issue.However the permission shall"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "       have to be revalidated before the expiry of the above period on payment of such fee as may be prescribed under"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "       rules and such revalidation shall be valid for one year"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "8.   (i) Approval of plans and acceptance of any statement or document pertaining to such plan shall not exempt"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "      the owner or person or persons under whose supervision the building is constructed from their responsibilities"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "      imposed under ODA (Planning & Building Standards) Rules 2020, or under any other law for the time being in"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "      force."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "      (ii) Approval of plan would mean granting of permission to construct under these regulations in force only"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "       and shall not mean among other things-"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (a) The title over the land or building"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (b) Easement rights"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (c) Variation in area from recorded area of a plot or a building"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (d) Structural stability"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (e) Workmanship and soundness of materials used in the construction of the buildings"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (f) Quality of building services and amenities in the construction of the building,"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (g) the site/area liable to flooding as a result of not taking proper drainage arrangement as per the natural"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            lay of the land, etc and"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (h) Other requirements or licenses or clearances required to be obtained for the site /premises or activity"
          }
