        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            under various other laws."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "9.   In case of any dispute arising out of land record or in respect of right, title, interest after this permission is"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "        granted, the permission so granted shall be treated as automatically cancelled during the period of dispute."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "10.   Neither granting of the permit nor the approval of the drawing and specifications, nor inspections made by the"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "        Authority during erection of the building shall in any way relieve the owner of such building from full"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "        responsibility for carrying out the work in accordance with the requirements of NBC 2005 and these regulations."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "11.   The owner /applicant shall;",
            "bold": true
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (a) Permit the Authority to enter the building or premises, for which the permission has been granted at any"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            reasonable time for the purpose of enforcing the regulations;"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (b) Obtain, wherever applicable, from the competent Authority permissions/clearance required in connection"
          }
