        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            Technical persons engaged by him."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "            (d) Obtain an Occupancy Certificate from the Authority prior to occupation of building in full or part."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "12.   The applicant shall abide by the provisions of Rule no.15 of ODA (P&BS)Rules, 2020 with regard to third party",
            "bold": true
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
