            "bold": true
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "        provision of the same.",
            "bold": true
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "13.   (a) In case the full plot or part thereof on which permission is accorded is agricultural kisam, the same may be"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "         converted to non-agricultural kisam under section8 of OLR Act before commencement of construction."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "        (b) The owner/applicant shall get the structural plan and design vetted by the institutions identified by the"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "          Authority for buildings more than 30 mtr height before commencement of construction."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
