        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "         records of the test data shall be kept available for inspection during the construction of building and for such"
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "         period thereafter as required by the Authority."
          }
        ],
        "style": "small-text-no-margin"
      },
      {
        "text": [
          {
            "text": "15.   The persons to whom a permit is issued during construction shall keep pasted in a conspicuous place on the"
